                  },
                  "name": "Player Core",
                  "page": 282,
                  "type": "source"
                }
              ],
              "text": "The fatal trait includes a die size. On a critical hit, the weapon\u2019s damage die increases to that die size instead of the normal die size, and the weapon adds one additional damage die of the listed size.",
